data.value: 4 November 1998. With the very first light of dawn, Prothom Alo (The First Light), started its humble journey. Because of its courageous journalism, rich content, and presentation with unique layout and design, Prothom Alo quickly won the hearts of people, even the most sophisticated and fastidious readers extended their loyalty toward it. Since then, Prothom Alo has been lighting up every nook and corner of Bangladesh along with 200 other countries and territories across the world through its print and digital offerings.
